data.description: Wouldn't it be nice to live in a nice, quant neighborhood near the Coast?  Where you can park your boat in the driveway without being harassed? Welcome to 369 Goodman...where you can have all of that and more without the hefty price tag! Beautiful home with LVP throughout and no carpet to be found anywhere! Full of natural lighting and high ceilings. Gourmet kitchen has recess lighting, custom cabinetry, stainless appliances, two pantries and center island with electricity and storage.  Master bedroom and 2 other bedrooms are downstairs (one being used as a playroom) with 2 full baths! Upstairs is a Bonus room with full bath, walk in attic access and a balcony! Perfect for teenager or in-law suite. Home is complete with a 2 car garage, irrigation system in the front yard, extended driveway for guests and a private screened in rear porch. Amenity packed community to include a marina, clubhouse and pool. Not in a flood zone! Welcome Home!
